  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Acid is a psychotropic puzzle as players get to fire a pulse of light at the psychedelic conundrums by charging the correct distance and then aim, a little like a golf game gone wrong. Great Tempest style visuals with kanji characters and neon tracers. A fine off kilter title well worth tuning in to.",
